Comment: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,【夜斗 四季無休!】
Comment: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,【無論有何種煩惱{\rsymbol}…{\r}】
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.33,0:04:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 可惡 伴音那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.76,0:05:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然真的辭去神器一職了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.90,0:05:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呼 哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.50,0:05:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿呦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.23,0:05:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉 就這麼點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.66,0:05:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不夠建神社的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.08,0:05:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs30\pos(640,5)}夜斗 四季無休!\N無論有何種煩惱都立刻為您解決!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.41,0:05:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說 建神社之前要先找到新的神器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.66,0:05:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算我是個神明
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.27,0:05:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有神器也等於手無寸鐵{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.87,0:05:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對{\rsymbol}…{\r}應該叫一絲不掛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.80,0:05:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去要是有了委託{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.37,0:05:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘛{\rsymbol}…{\r}雖說本來就見不到什麼委託{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.86,0:05:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您好 謝謝您選擇了本神明
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.84,0:05:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是快捷便宜又放心的外派神明夜斗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.51,0:05:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.29,0:05:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上主大人失蹤了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.86,0:05:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn方正中雅宋_GBK\fs40\c&H000000&\fsp8\bord0.1\blur4\3a&HA0\pos(984,654)}家貓與流浪神與尾巴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.84,0:05:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上主大人?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.03,0:05:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\bord0\c&H232323&\pos(653,104)}名字：上主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.03,0:05:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\bord0\c&H0F0F0F&\pos(639,450)}尋找迷途貓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.32,0:05:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還真有給寵物起這種名字的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.41,0:05:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像閣下大人 國王大人 神明大人什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.03,0:05:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神明大人{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.24,0:06:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞美不也給自家狗起了個蛋疼名字嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.62,0:06:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用Zenny領隊的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.81,0:06:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡蛋疼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.08,0:06:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,椎名君可是我的夢中情人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.01,0:06:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得百鬼夜行才是神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.69,0:06:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,視覺系哪裡好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.91,0:06:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上主大人 上主大人
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.22,0:06:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34}你那個Zenny到底哪裡好了啊\N{\r}\h
Dialogue: 1,0:06:12.46,0:06:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34}Zenny可是神\N{\r}\h
Dialogue: 1,0:06:14.11,0:06:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34}神都是百鬼夜行\N{\r}\h
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.53,0:06:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上主大人喂
Comment: 0,0:06:16.87,0:06:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちょっと　ひおり
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.16,0:06:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得哪個才是神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.33,0:06:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神的下載結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.82,0:06:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位 世紀的決戰拖入了最後一回合
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.35,0:06:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雙方都找尋著出手時機{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.80,0:06:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天啊 腿被抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.86,0:06:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,螳野要怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.86,0:06:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.54,0:06:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勝負已分
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.38,0:06:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一擊叢林迴旋踢制勝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.42,0:06:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我們問你真是蠢透了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.40,0:06:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為日和是個隱秘型的搏擊粉絲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.17,0:06:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這個還能算隱秘嗎{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.68,0:06:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒跟父母說過吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.69,0:06:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是知道我有這種愛好 母親一定會昏過去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.74,0:07:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太野蠻了
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.74,0:07:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34}上主大人\N{\r}\h
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.44,0:07:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要成為不辱一岐家名聲的謙謙淑女才行
Dialogue: 1,0:07:01.74,0:07:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34}上主大人\N{\r}\h
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.48,0:07:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34}上主大人\N{\r}\h
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.07,0:07:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您到底在哪裡啊
Dialogue: 1,0:07:04.89,0:07:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34}然後找一名金龜婿\N{\r}\h
Dialogue: 1,0:07:08.18,0:07:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34}你們兩個為什麼知道我母親的說話口氣啊\N{\r}\h
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.89,0:07:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.27,0:07:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.25,0:07:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊 日和
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.67,0:07:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你除了螳野就不喜歡別的男人了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.26,0:07:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊是啊 就是那種稍微纖細點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.87,0:07:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能成為賢胥良夫的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.73,0:07:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.66,0:07:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃{\rsymbol}…{\r}唔{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.53,0:07:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡的人啊{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.12,0:07:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡的人什麼的{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.99,0:07:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.26,0:07:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等等 站住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.38,0:07:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別逃啊 上主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.35,0:07:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.65,0:08:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日和
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.85,0:08:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.95,0:08:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有個女孩子突然衝出來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.15,0:08:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也太危險了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.78,0:08:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然衝到馬路中間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.35,0:08:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死掉了怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.41,0:08:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.21,0:08:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倒是你{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.93,0:08:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日和 日和
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.74,0:08:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,振作點啊 日和
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.40,0:08:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日和
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.29,0:08:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.86,0:08:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我剛叫了救護車
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.56,0:08:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.99,0:08:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.18,0:08:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒!!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.74,0:08:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒!!!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.39,0:08:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日和 能聽到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.46,0:08:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日和
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.26,0:08:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日和
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.36,0:08:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 醒過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.60,0:08:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.50,0:08:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有哪裡痛嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.82,0:08:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老公 快診查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.86,0:08:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.12,0:09:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 看來沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.12,0:09:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.26,0:09:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.36,0:09:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,CT也顯示沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,腦波也很正常
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.55,0:09:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被公交車撞倒 竟然只受了擦傷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.80,0:09:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被公交車{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.83,0:09:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老公 擔心死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.05,0:09:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日和寶貴的身體要是有個三長兩短
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.21,0:09:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是咱家的醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.72,0:09:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就讓她住一陣子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.52,0:09:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.84,0:09:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有很多病人等著空床位哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.32,0:09:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.70,0:09:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起被撞的男生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.13,0:09:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 有的{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.73,0:09:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是有{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.22,0:09:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒?沒那麼個人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.88,0:09:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回過神時日和已經倒在地上了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.06,0:09:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.51,0:09:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日和的意識可能還不太清醒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.18,0:09:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 確實有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.52,0:09:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,睏了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.98,0:09:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是累了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.41,0:09:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天就好好睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.08,0:10:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確實有一個男生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.53,0:10:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且 那時
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.80,0:10:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好像看到了另一個我{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.96,0:10:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還想活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.96,0:10:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好想見那個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.12,0:10:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候才能從這出去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.39,0:10:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.18,0:10:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.46,0:10:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.31,0:10:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去恐怕{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.14,0:10:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等你養好病就帶你出去玩哦
Dialogue: 1,0:10:50.20,0:10:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34}這聲音是什麼{\rsymbol\fs34}…{\r}\N{\r}\h
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.98,0:10:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喘不過{\rsymbol}…{\r}喘不過氣來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.02,0:10:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好疼{\rsymbol}…{\r}好疼啊
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.69,0:10:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34}好想出去玩啊\N{\r}\h
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.64,0:11:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.35,0:11:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能聽到彼岸的聲音嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.31,0:11:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能這麼靈活 看來不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.04,0:11:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊{\rsymbol}…{\r}你是今早的{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.20,0:11:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那時謝謝咯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.65,0:11:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 其實那輛車我能躲開
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.70,0:11:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過還是第一次有人類來救我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.56,0:11:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你{\rsymbol}…{\r}你是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.96,0:11:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是神明
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.51,0:11:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 是警察嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.17,0:11:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個{\rsymbol}…{\r}有個稱自己是神明的身穿運動衫的{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.44,0:11:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢著慢著慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.84,0:11:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是如假包換的八百萬神之一
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.47,0:11:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夜斗神
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.33,0:11:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夜斗神?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.89,0:12:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒聽過這種神明
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.26,0:12:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一次都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.46,0:12:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 雖然目前是個絕讚推銷中的流浪漢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.04,0:12:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞧著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.68,0:12:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很快會讓名字響徹四海
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.93,0:12:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成為受眾人叩拜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.28,0:12:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萬眾祈求 萬眾祈願的神明
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.94,0:12:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.58,0:12:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢耶 噢耶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.68,0:12:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萬歲 萬歲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.85,0:12:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終有一天站到這國家的頂點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.69,0:12:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今夜將有時化啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.99,0:12:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是它們的巢穴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.06,0:12:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如今沒有神器
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.51,0:12:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不宜久留
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.60,0:12:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,何況野良今晚也在使用中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.78,0:12:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等 那是給我的探病禮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.56,0:12:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你 叫什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.56,0:12:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日和
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.90,0:12:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一岐日和
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.77,0:13:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日和
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.96,0:13:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我確認過你的平安了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.17,0:13:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下兩清了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.74,0:13:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見咯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.04,0:13:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.01,0:13:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身體好重
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.55,0:13:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,意識有些{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.92,0:13:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夜{\rsymbol}…{\r}斗{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.64,0:13:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日和
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.06,0:13:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞美 小山
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.21,0:13:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經不要緊了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.70,0:13:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.24,0:13:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你沒事真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.76,0:13:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉哦 讓你們擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.96,0:13:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次你要是再往馬路中間衝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.82,0:13:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就用叢林迴旋踢教訓你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.97,0:13:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是螳野大人踢的也許求之不得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.92,0:13:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.82,0:13:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 日和
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.62,0:13:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.76,0:13:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知怎的偶爾會很睏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.20,0:13:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.83,0:13:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通宵打遊戲了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.00,0:14:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個{\rsymbol}…{\r}是個夢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.93,0:14:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那天夜裡 在病房
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.81,0:14:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好像遇到了誰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.86,0:14:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,運動衫{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.56,0:14:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊吧 日和
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.36,0:14:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你今天一天都晃晃悠悠的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.35,0:14:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯{\rsymbol}…{\r}總是有些睏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.10,0:14:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住院時睡太多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.08,0:14:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟剛出過車禍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.14,0:14:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 日和
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.05,0:14:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\bord0\c&H232323&\pos(647,128)}名字：上主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.05,0:14:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\bord0\c&H232323&\pos(650,445)}尋找迷途貓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.50,0:14:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.24,0:14:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是之前那個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.80,0:14:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.78,0:14:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我記得追這隻貓的時候 也有個穿運動衫的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.02,0:14:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.57,0:14:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 你們倆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.04,0:15:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.33,0:15:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.72,0:15:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,需即刻去尋上主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.20,0:15:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.85,0:15:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.31,0:15:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.44,0:15:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上主大人?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.16,0:15:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.26,0:15:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.77,0:15:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要找到那隻貓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.45,0:15:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許就能徹底想起來了
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.32,0:15:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34}上主大人\N{\r}\h
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.70,0:15:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.75,0:15:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又犯睏{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.76,0:15:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個氣味{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.26,0:15:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 上主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.68,0:15:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞧哦 這裡有木天蓼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.17,0:16:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的要起時化了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.78,0:16:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.19,0:16:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.88,0:16:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.11,0:16:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要跑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.28,0:16:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.99,0:16:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔 怎麼了怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.64,0:16:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好香
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.25,0:16:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好香好香
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.03,0:16:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好香好香好香{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.02,0:16:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好香
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.94,0:16:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是雜魚 但數量太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.98,0:16:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對付起來就沒完沒了了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.18,0:16:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說你 逗它們來著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.47,0:16:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.58,0:16:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您還真喜歡玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.27,0:16:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好香
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.30,0:17:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進去呆著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.90,0:17:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘁 沒效果
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.78,0:17:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 伴器
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.01,0:17:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 現在沒有神器來著{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.35,0:17:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一岐日和?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.56,0:17:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.87,0:17:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忍無可忍啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.33,0:17:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.56,0:17:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叢林{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.46,0:17:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迴旋踢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.40,0:18:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有{\rsymbol}…{\r}有效果
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.74,0:18:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有螳野大人靈魂附體了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.42,0:18:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的王 我要一生追隨你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.89,0:18:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算是逃掉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.58,0:18:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 這個女的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.49,0:18:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又救了我一次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.34,0:18:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終於見到你了啊 夜斗先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.90,0:18:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還有很多事想問你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.90,0:18:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是你一下子就走掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.34,0:18:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次請不要糊弄我 要好好回答
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.30,0:18:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.60,0:18:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,靈魂跑出來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.67,0:18:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.60,0:19:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身體掛在那邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.70,0:19:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.55,0:19:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個是我?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.11,0:19:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.71,0:19:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我死掉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.51,0:19:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.28,0:19:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本體只是在睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.16,0:19:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.93,0:19:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是個招什麼貓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.39,0:19:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽明天也會去貼傳單找的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.14,0:19:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.27,0:19:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.51,0:19:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定會找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.85,0:19:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.04,0:19:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.11,0:19:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.27,0:19:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是上主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.50,0:19:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.30,0:20:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,願望真的成真了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.50,0:20:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 夜斗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.22,0:20:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好聞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.42,0:20:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,討厭 放開我 變態
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.11,0:20:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是變態 是神明
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.81,0:20:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又說什麼神明
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.28,0:20:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 尾巴{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.98,0:20:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧? 沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.90,0:20:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.32,0:20:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全都是夢?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.50,0:20:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肯定不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.97,0:20:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我{\rsymbol}…{\r}我的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.06,0:20:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.03,0:20:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概是因為車禍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.30,0:20:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人們生活生息在此岸 與之相對的是彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.10,0:20:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如今的你 變成了生活在兩者縫隙間的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.23,0:20:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,此岸和彼岸?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.32,0:20:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 這個彼岸呢 嘛{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.70,0:20:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用你們的話說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.02,0:20:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是地府
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.79,0:20:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你雖然活著 卻成了『妖』
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.49,0:21:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妖?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.96,0:21:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是人的念想凝聚結合具化成型
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.06,0:21:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,附在人的身上作惡的那類傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.84,0:21:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫非{\rsymbol}…{\r}剛才那隻大青蛙也是{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.45,0:21:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是妖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.56,0:21:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和那個成同類了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.90,0:21:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不太一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.28,0:21:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是更半吊子的那種
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.87,0:21:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個{\rsymbol}…{\r}我不太懂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.20,0:21:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你變成了經常靈魂出竅的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.98,0:21:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說{\rsymbol}…{\r}怎麼才能治好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.19,0:21:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,治好? 可能嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.29,0:21:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你已經變成了這種體質
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.40,0:21:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放棄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.39,0:21:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.59,0:21:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很困擾誒 我不要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.58,0:21:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把我變回去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.95,0:21:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夜斗先生是神明對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.65,0:21:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幫幫我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.27,0:21:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿錢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.08,0:21:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還要錢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.19,0:21:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不廢話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.21,0:21:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪有不花錢就實現的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.85,0:21:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿這個數我就幫你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.59,0:21:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五{\rsymbol}…{\r}五萬?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.93,0:21:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五十萬?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.90,0:21:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種天文數字{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.07,0:21:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘁 傻蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.69,0:21:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可是神明
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.82,0:22:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,香油錢當然是五日元啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.79,0:22:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.96,0:22:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊{\rsymbol}…{\r}那個{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.17,0:22:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.95,0:22:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我確實聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.67,0:22:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一岐日和
